snippet.title: Here's Why Some People Think Melania Trump May Divorce Donald
snippet.description:
They've been married since 2005, but Donald and Melania Trump don't always seem like they're going to stand the test of time. The 2016 presidential election season is when rumors really started circulating that Melania Trump might not be happily betrothed. While some people close to the couple, like Donald's former attorney Michael Cohen, claim that they're actually two peas in a pod, the seemingly cold reception Melania gave Donald during his presidency raises quite a few questions … "Why won't she hold his hand?" being the main one. Are the Trumps destined for a split? Or are they meant to be? Here's why some people think Melania Trump may divorce Donald.
